high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the wooden shelves, head right at the door and walk to the wooden desk.
Pick up the gray bowl in front of the small lamp on the desk.
Turn around, hang a left at the bed, take a right at the wall and walk to the wooden shelves on the wall.
Put the gray bowl on the bottom middle shelf to the left of the watch.
Pick up the watch to the right of the gray bowl on the shelf.
Put the watch inside the gray bowl on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a watch on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and go toward the shelves, then turn left and move forward, then turn right to go to the desk with the lamp on it.
Pick up the bowl from the desk.
Turn around and go forward to the bed, then turn left and go to the wall, then turn right to go to the shelves ahead.
Put the bowl on the bottom shelf.
Pick up the watch on the bottom shelf.
Put the watch in the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with the watch in it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk three steps then turn right and walk to the desk between the two black chairs.
Pick up the bowl that's in front of you under the light.
Turnaround and walk to the bed then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the shelves.
Put the bowl on the shelf to the left of the watch.
Put the watch in the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a watch in a bowl on the shelf.
